data.description: Conveniently located close to Tomball, Magnolia and the Woodlands. Nestled in Stagecoach Farms, a serene restricted neighborhood filled with wildlife, trees, parks and picturesque lakes. 3 bedrooms, 1 Theater/Game Room (the surround system will stay in the home), 2 full baths, 1 half baths, nine-foot ceilings, family area, garage painted with epoxy floor, alarm system and video cameras (stay in the home). Enjoy the spacious backyard with nice fireplace and beautiful pergola. Cozy home has been freshly painted in 2023. On a 15,000 SQFT lot high and dry.
